). The MIC value of amoxicillin for Escherichia coli ATCC25922 increased eight times (32 µg/mL) by the 10th generation, 256 times (1024 µg/mL) by the 20th generation, and 512 times (2048 µg/mL) by the 40th to 150th generations (
